              <li>Wheel Size: 28 inches</li>
              <li>Rims: Aluminum</li>
          </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="content-sandman4" style="display: none;">
          <h2>Sandman 4 - Compliance Information</h2>
          <ul>
              <li>Weight: 9.8kg</li>
              <li>Gear: Shimano GRX 400</li>
              <li>Gears: 20</li>
              <li>Frame: TORAY T800 Carbon</li>
              <li>Brakes: Hydraulic</li>
